Subprog AS_POP(VALEUR)
Variable Char    VALEUR()
Local Integer INDIC : INDIC = indice
Raz mkstat
Call TEXTE(45582,GBOUT1) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(6028,GBOUTS) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(12276,GBOUTP) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(16134,GBOUTA) From OBJDIV
## Action STD
Call AS_POP(VALEUR) From SUBORA
If mkstat=2
 [M]POP(INDIC) = VALEUR
 Affzo POP(INDIC) : mkstat = 2
Endif
Onkey 129 Titled GBOUT1 Call B1_POP(zc) From W1ORA0
Onkey   2 Titled GBOUTS Call S_POP(zc) From W1ORA0
Onkey 144 Titled GBOUTP Call P_POP(zc) From W1ORA0
Onkey 146 Titled GBOUTA Call SA_POP(zc) From W1ORA0
